name: Mirror of the Soul
description:
"We are Humans, 
Superiorly intelligent specie, 
The only one of our kind.
Adorned perfectly with so much confidence & pride.
Like diamonds from the rough,
Carved into our very best parts.
Giving us unquestionable uniqueness.
Priceless & of great & immense value.
Gifted power over all the universe.
We falter & sometimes forget to shine brighter than the stars.
But engraved in us is unwavering resilience & valor to overcome all that challenges us.
We are Humans, 
The only one of our kind."

"Mirror of the Soul" part of the "Human Elements" Set by Butu | Writings by @karl_maz
